&lt;p data-start=&quot;156&quot; data-end=&quot;487&quot;&gt;Are you passionate about solving complex challenges in the fintech space? We’re looking for a Business Development Representative (BDR) to join our dynamic startup, backed by Sequoia Capital. We’re building the universal payment layer to unify all currencies - fiat and crypto - so businesses and consumers can transact seamlessly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;489&quot; data-end=&quot;988&quot;&gt;In this role, you’ll be responsible for generating pipeline and driving top-of-funnel growth through high-impact outbound prospecting. You’ll work closely with sales and marketing to test and refine messaging, break through the noise with creative outreach, and connect with decision-makers. This is a highly execution-focused role where your work will directly impact revenue. If you thrive in fast-paced environments and love turning cold outreach into meaningful conversations, we’d love to chat.&lt;/p&gt;
