&lt;p data-start=&quot;1412&quot; data-end=&quot;1517&quot;&gt;Own the &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1420&quot; data-end=&quot;1478&quot;&gt;0→1 development and launch of our card issuing program&lt;/strong&gt;, including physical and virtual cards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;n3p0mu&quot; data-start=&quot;1518&quot; data-end=&quot;1638&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1520&quot; data-end=&quot;1638&quot;&gt;Define and execute the &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1543&quot; data-end=&quot;1575&quot;&gt;card issuing product roadmap&lt;/strong&gt;, from infrastructure and integrations to user-facing features.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1r8fy0k&quot; data-start=&quot;1639&quot; data-end=&quot;1771&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1641&quot; data-end=&quot;1771&quot;&gt;Work closely with &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1659&quot; data-end=&quot;1733&quot;&gt;issuing banks, payment processors, and card networks (Visa/Mastercard)&lt;/strong&gt; to launch and scale our card program.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
