&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure as Code&lt;/strong&gt; - Manage GCP resources; embed security, IAM least-privilege, and cost controls by default.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance &amp;amp; cost tuning&lt;/strong&gt; - Profile hot paths (BigQuery, Firestore, Pub/Sub), and implement caching or concurrency improvements to keep user latency &amp;lt; 100 ms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developer tooling&lt;/strong&gt; - Eliminate toil by improving local-to-prod parity, secrets management, and spinning up environments with a single command.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Culture carrier&lt;/strong&gt; - Instill reliability thinking across engineering and product as the first platform-focused hire.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
